  "title": "Temporary Sales Merchandiser (4–6 Months Contract)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Duration:</strong> 4–6 months (to cover staff on medical leave)<br /><strong>Location:</strong> Singapore (office Ang Mo Kio; reporting not required daily)<br /><strong>Employment Type:</strong> Contract</p><ul><li><strong>Working Hours:</strong> 8:30 AM – 5:15 PM, Monday to Friday</li><li><strong>Basic Salary:</strong> $2,300 per month</li><li><strong>Transport Allowance:</strong> $200 per month</li><li><strong>Mobile Allowance:</strong> $50 per month</li></ul><p><strong>Product Category</strong></p><ul><li>Baby care products such as toiletries, wipes, and related items.</li></ul><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Travel to assigned retail outlets (e.g., supermarkets, Kiddy Palace, Sheng Siong, etc.) to ensure product availability.</li><li>Replenish stock on shelves and storage areas to maintain optimal product levels.</li><li>Raise orders with retailers when stock is low and follow up on delivery.</li><li>Set up and maintain product displays according to company standards.</li><li>Monitor competitor activities and provide feedback to the sales team.</li><li>Build and maintain good working relationships with store staff.</li><li>Report daily activities and stock status to the supervisor.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Prior experience in merchandising or retail sales preferred, especially in FMCG or baby care products.</li><li>Good communication and interpersonal skills.</li><li>Physically fit to handle stock replenishment and display setup.</li><li>Able to travel across multiple retail locations daily.</li><li>Independent, reliable, and able to manage time effectively.</li></ul><p>Interested applicants, please email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:lilian@juhlerprofessionals.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">lilian@juhlerprofessionals.com.sg</a></p><p>Tan Li Lian</p><p>EA 01C3135</p><p>Reg R1100465</p>",
